                                    <li><span class="font-bold text-lg text-red-600 mr-2">−</span> S + did not + V1</li>
                                    <li><span class="font-bold text-lg text-blue-600 mr-2">?</span> Did + S + V1?</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
